## üîß Architecture Notes
- Backend: Python (FastAPI)
- Frontend: React + Tailwind, mobile-first and responsive
- WhatsApp Bot: Twilio-based, reusing a prior tested deployment setup
- CI/CD: Ongoing, uses an existing deploy pipeline
- Deployment: Google Cloud Platform
- Architecture: Microservices architecture, all in a single repository
- Documentation: Developed continuously throughout the 12 weeks
- Presentations: Weekly internal presentations to stakeholders
- Auth System: Pending ‚Äî may integrate with a proprietary API from the client
- Excel Data: Awaiting real sales files from the client for format and schema
- Design: Developer-driven (no external mockups); client-side frontend has company guideline reference visuals
- Admin Roles: Staff and Admin roles with segmented admin capabilities
- Prize Stock: Not tracked in-system ‚Äî physical/experience prizes manually stocked, digital codes are on-demand

